## Grafo de Dependencias entre Squads

```
Squad Infra (F1)
  └→ Squad Auth (F2)
       ├→ Squad BPM (F3)
       │    └→ Squad Reference Data (F4A) ←──┐
       │    └→ Squad Clients (F4A) ←─────────┤ (usam reference data)
       │    └→ Squad Suppliers (F4A) ←───────┘
       │         └→ Squad Products (F4B)
       │         └→ Squad Quotations (F4B)
       │         └→ Squad Orders (F4B) ←── modulo central
       │         └→ Squad Search (F4B)
       │              └→ Squad Financial (F4C)
       │              └→ Squad Production (F4C)
       │              └→ Squad Requisitions (F4C)
       │              └→ Squad Dashboards (F4C)
       │              └→ Squad Reports (F4C)
       │                   └→ Squad Sync PF (F5)
       │
       └→ Squad Frontend Shell (F6) ←── pode iniciar apos F2
            ├→ Squad FE Sidebar (F6) ←── feature squad, dono da sidebar
            └→ Squad FE Home + Clients (F7A)
                 └→ Squad FE Orders (F7B) ←── MVP
                      ├→ Squad FE Products (F7C)
                      ├→ Squad FE Suppliers + Quotations (F7C)
                      ├→ Squad FE Requisitions (F7C)
                      ├→ Squad FE Financial (F7C)
                      ├→ Squad FE Production (F7C)
                      │    └→ Squad FE Dashboards + Reports (F7D)
                      │    └→ Squad FE Sync + Settings (F7D)
                      │         └→ Squad Polish & QA (F8)
```

---

## Protocolo de Interacao entre Squads

1. **Preciso de algo que pertence a outro squad:** Consulta o skill file do squad dono → identifica o membro responsavel → solicita via PR ou issue
2. **Meu trabalho afeta outro squad:** Verifica no mapa de dependencias acima quais squads dependem do meu → comunica a mudanca antes de mergear
3. **Conflito no schema Prisma:** Squad que adiciona o model e dono. Se dois squads precisam do mesmo model → quem tem mais campos e o dono, outro squad solicita adição
4. **Duvida sobre spec:** Consulta PLANO.md. Se a resposta nao esta la → escala para o Product Owner

